            We value your privacy<br/> <small>Privacy Policy</small>
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-lg-12">
       <h3><span class="text-left" style="color: #2a6496;padding-right: 20px;"><i class="glyphicon glyphicon-ok"></i></span><span class="text-center" >Pocket Recruiter</span></h3>
